-- MOVES-StanChart appoints Henrik Raber head of capital markets
-- 
-- Fri Aug 01, 2014 10:36AM EDT
-- None



Aug 1 (Reuters) - Standard Chartered Bank <STAN.L> named Henrik Raber head of capital markets, effective Aug. 16.

Raber, who will be based in Singapore, will report to Mark Dowie, acting group head of financial markets. Raber is currently head of debt capital markets.